# dist/ is built output — ignored by the root .gitignore. The v0.5 model
# of committing the precompiled bundle is replaced in the monorepo by
# either `agent-pack/install.sh` rebuilding on install, or the Tauri
# bundle shipping its own assets (see LLD Phase 2 § D9).
